== Umugambi ==
Jay ( Chris Attoh ), casanova, yatunguye inshuti ze, arasaba umukunzi we Kimora (Yvonne Nelson). Inshuti ya Jay, Raymond ( Kweku Elliot ) casanova ubu nawe yashakanye n'umwe mu nshuti za Kimora, Paula ( Nadia Buari ), ntabyitayeho<ref>Waiting for Yvonne Nelson's complicated Single and Married ... <nowiki>https://www.vanguardngr.com</nowiki> › ... › Showtime People</ref>. Andy (Eddie Watson), "mubi" muri batatu, atekereza ko Jay ari hafi gufungwa ubuzima bwe bwose<ref>Pascal Amanfo Net Worth And Biography. - The360Report <nowiki>https://the360report.com</nowiki> › pascal-amanfo-net-worth-an...</ref>.

Umwaka umwe nyuma yubukwe, Jay araryamana na Judith (Jane Awindor ), kandi ahora abeshya Kimora<ref>Pascal Amanfo Net Worth 2021 | Glusea.com <nowiki>https://www.glusea.com</nowiki> › pascal-amanfo-net-worth</ref>. Jay amaherezo aratandukana na we, kuko yamutunze cyane; asohoka mu nzu ye, Jay yikubita kuri Raymond, na we usohoka mu nzu ya nyirabuja, bityo amenya amabanga ya mugenzi we<ref name=":0" />. Ikigaragara ni uko Paula, umunyamategeko, ahora ahugiye mu kazi kandi ntajya abona umwanya wa Raymond, mu gihe Kimora na we yanze guha Jay. Paula ahura Raymond na Yolanda (Itz Tiffany), inshuti ye ishaje, maze Raymond atangira gukundana nawe<ref name=":1" />.

